Test Script for an Inventory System

1. Adding a New Item

- Create a new item
- Verify that new item is added to the inventory list
- Create a new item with invalid inputs
- Verify that the inventory list is not update
- Test for updating existing items

2. Update an existing Item

- Choose an existing item from the inventory list
- Update the item with valid inputs
- Verify that the item details are updated in the inventory list
- Try to update the item with invalid inputs
- Verify that the item details are not updated with the invalid inputs

3. Delete an Item

- Choose an existing item from the inventory list
- Delete the item
- Verify that the item is no longer in the inventory list
- Try to delete an item that doesn't exist
- Verify that the inventory list is not changed